{"title":"老家（外一首）","authors":["卢晓圣"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":9,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"老家（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卢晓圣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜鹊在巢外鸣叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛羊在圈里吃草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炊烟在房上升起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间忙了一天的乡亲踏上了归途。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"知足未必全在乎钞票，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一家人大大小小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃饱便喜上眉梢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邻居间彼此串门说笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子们结伴成群嬉闹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁家日子有点起色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那就添件电视机瞧瞧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旱烟叶似乎受了潮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呛人的烟味人人能闻到。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙子抽烟把牌子炫耀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘的新衣舍不得穿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看又包上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"偶尔也喝杯茶水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"味苦便说是最好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天还没黑多久，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小孩便闹着睡觉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大人还没有躺下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就想着明天得起早。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳月亮相互偶尔一道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看着山乡的几孔石桥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山乡行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有三个人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从山乡走过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一个人看到眼里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记在心里的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫穷  落后  荒凉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第二个人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看到眼里记在心里的是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"空气的纯净"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山林的青翠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山里人的自由"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山里姑娘的美丽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第三个人来过几次"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他看到的是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山里的矿藏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剩余劳动力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有火种般的各种潜能"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}